  <summary date="2017-04-28T04:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Repeal of the Obamacare Bay State Boondoogle Act

This bill&#160;requires that&#160;the Medicare hospital wage index floor for non-rural areas be calculated&#160;using state-specific, rather than national, budget neutrality. (The Medicare hospital wage index is used to calculate geographic adjustments to Medicare reimbursements.)</summary>
